packs.name: Venturecraft
packs.description:
Here's an early beta version of a huge structure datapack I'm making. Right now these are some small structures. There are some big dungeons and things to explore being worked on.


Post any structure suggestions in the comments!
If I use one of the ideas you come up with, I will shout you out(if you want) in the video when this datapack's full version comes out!
